{"tid":1098730,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]earth force defense討論區及報價區","createTime":"2019-04-09T09:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T08:40:58.000Z","uid":247435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74d3396d0cf364ca14734fecdb11536902c78453","tid":1098730,"uid":247435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E1giifc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE1giifc.jpg&h=61f74418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=174640\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fgnn%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D174640&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=3d5701c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/gnn/detail.php?sn=174640</a><br />\n<br />\n下面係由巴哈論壇所整理出黎的情報<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=10135&amp;snA=295&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D10135%26snA%3D295%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3D&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=81cd77a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=10135&amp;snA=295&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=</a><br />\n<br />\n新作IRON RAIN(下稱IR)的多國語言版跟日版同步於4月11日推出，可見D3P對此作很重視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nEDF粉相信不會猶豫直接會衝首發，但畢竟IR不是正傳系列作，<br />\n<br />\n在現時有限的情報下似乎有些值得討論或者觀望的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先關於連線協力人數，以上連結(巴哈新聞)是寫線上1-6人。如果是戰役模式都能全程1-6人就實在太好。不過按照舊作決戰昆蟲來看，暫不排除所謂1-6人協力是指生存模式(WAVE SURVIVE一類)。戰役仍是3-4人這樣。當然官方暫時沒有公佈生存模式之類。戰役模式1-6人仍是有希望。<br />\n<br />\n至於官網寫連線1-8人是因為還有個Mercenary mode(傭兵模式?)，是一個可供8人參與的PVP模式。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看一下終極版的內容有一堆痛車，但IR並沒有空襲兵，是否意味所有兵科都能呼叫載具值得期待。但如果可以叫載具，騎兵操縱怪物會不會沒太大意義?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n值得留意是有遊戲貸貨幣DLC，用途是換取裝備和道具。這麼一來IR裝備可能不是直接農出來╴而是靠刷錢買。好處是只要付出時間就一定可以取得指定裝備，還能決定取得的先後次序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看到國外論壇IR長任務似乎有50多個，比決戰昆蟲30個左右更豐富，算是合理的長度。本傳100多個任務太多了，有不少濫竽充數的任務。希望IR的任務能令人印象深刻一些。"},{"pid":"345cb05748cea6fdbf730b2df400aa6aa900a6a2","tid":1098730,"uid":247435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4Huw70pftYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4Huw70pftYg&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=74413eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4Huw70pftYg</a><br />\n<br />\nign first 90mins gameplay"},{"pid":"700a0513b8126b56357cf186e3a2003127c00ba9","tid":1098730,"uid":247435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1098487/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1098487/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n另有ps4約戰whatsapp約戰群組，歡迎加入"},{"pid":"ec0b02c8d9f0d962de9d39c2bb585dd7d864e971","tid":1098730,"uid":247435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"700a0513b8126b56357cf186e3a2003127c00ba9","tid":1098730,"uid":247435,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T09:26:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1098487/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1098487/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n另有ps4約戰whatsapp約戰群組，歡迎加入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T17:25:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2a31b41228505c32e282e4eef02b598dfa42e5a3","tid":1098730,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"無人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba03c4112ada14ef0201fee1f133c47b7a46d74","tid":1098730,"uid":247435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a31b41228505c32e282e4eef02b598dfa42e5a3","tid":1098730,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"無人氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"隻game未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，聽日可能會好d"},{"pid"